Python之字符串的遍历
1、第一种方式，for in

    girl_str = "love You"
     
    for everyChar in girl_str:
        print everyChar

2、第二种方式，range()或xrange（），把字符串长度传进去就行

    girl_str = "love You"
     
    for index in range(len(girl_str)):
        print girl_str[index]

3、第三种方式，enumerate()

    girl_str = "love You"
     
    for index, everyChar in enumerate(girl_str):
        print str(index) + everyChar

4、第四种方式，iter()，怒赞中

    girl_str = "love You"
     
    for everyChar in iter(girl_str):
        print everyChar
--------------------- 
